latestIgtvVideos.caption:
First Freestyle Competition.This was important. 

Exactly a year back 7th Dec, I started swinging on the bar and started with swing gainer, then moved on to 180's, and muscle up 360, back lever on the static side, then shrimp Flip which is always going to be special😌, then swing 360's and now working on registering all the moves.

When @musclebar.pune put up the categories, I was not sure if I want to participate, but definitely there was a bias that karna toh hai freestyle mein😬🤫, I knew it was going to be tough and I wasn't prepared enough, but it was all about starting somewhere as I say it's just as long as you don't start. 

Just a week before when I was in good form, I did register but that last week the rains hit due to which we couldn't do dynamics and my 360's hit low :( but I had to atleast finish what I started. So just went up there and did try my best, yes missed the grabs but *it's completely okay* not going to stress about it. Trust me, it's okay to fail, it's all part of the process. The support that the community has shown is immense and for this I would like to thank each one cheering and believing that I could do something out there. It feels great. ❤️

Never did I think a year back, this is where I will be and a huge thanks to the lockdown that hit and @cali1o1 and coaches there, that have given me one of the best learnings and support😌❤️.

With this, I really hope to see more woman freestylers coming up in India, fighting the fear and we got THISSSS!!!!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Handstand Attempts for the day🤸🏾‍♀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Just for being motivated😌, have been doing this for more than 3 years now, still don't have that hold, is it the patience? is the technique? is the just not the right time? I don't know, but I am definitely not giving up on this, 3 years toh aur ek aur hi sahi.

Aiming to get it by the end of the year🤸🏾‍♀️

Got good hold in the last two attempt (one of around 6s, the other was good because I didn't touch the wall while getting into the handstand🤸🏾‍♀️😌).

latestPosts.caption:
Equally proud of the failures as I'm of my success❤️

I failed this time at my combos which was the only thing I didn't want to happen, it was okay that I didn't have 540, but I didn't want to fail at what I have already, but I did fail. But not putting myself under a lot of stress, going to focus more on everything coming forward and work harder than ever and I hopefully do much better❤️🇮🇳⚡️

Thank you everyone who has been supporting me and sending me wishes, I'm sorry I couldn't give me my best but this pushes me even harder now.🥺❤️😭
